步骤1：安装redhat-lsb</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@Ansible ~]# ansible all -m yum -a &quot;name=redhat-lsb state=present&quot;</span><br><span class="line">36.103.245.138 | SUCCESS =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;changed&quot;: false, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;msg&quot;: &quot;&quot;, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;rc&quot;: 0, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;results&quot;: [</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;redhat-lsb-4.1-27.el7.centos.1.x86_64 providing redhat-lsb is already installed&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">36.103.245.70 | SUCCESS =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;changed&quot;: false, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;msg&quot;: &quot;&quot;, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;rc&quot;: 0, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;results&quot;: [</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;redhat-lsb-4.1-27.el7.centos.1.x86_64 providing redhat-lsb is already installed&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">36.103.245.135 | SUCCESS =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;changed&quot;: false, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;msg&quot;: &quot;&quot;, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;rc&quot;: 0, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;results&quot;: [</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;redhat-lsb-4.1-27.el7.centos.1.x86_64 providing redhat-lsb is already installed&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    ]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="步骤2：查看系统版本号"><a href="#步骤2：查看系统版本号" class="headerlink" title="步骤2：查看系统版本号"></a>步骤2：查看系统版本号</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@Ansible ~]# ansible all -m command -a &quot;lsb_release -a&quot;</span><br><span class="line">36.103.245.138 | SUCCESS | rc=0 &gt;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">LSB Version:    :core-4.1-amd64:core-4.1-noarch:cxx-4.1-amd64:cxx-4.1-noarch:desktop-4.1-amd64:desktop-4.1-noarch:languages-4.1-amd64:languages-4.1-noarch:printing-4.1-amd64:printing-4.1-noarch</span><br><span class="line">Distributor ID: CentOS</span><br><span class="line">Description:    CentOS Linux release 7.3.1611 (Core) </span><br><span class="line">Release:        7.3.1611</span><br><span class="line">Codename:       Core</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">36.103.245.70 | SUCCESS | rc=0 &gt;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">LSB Version:    :core-4.1-amd64:core-4.1-noarch:cxx-4.1-amd64:cxx-4.1-noarch:desktop-4.1-amd64:desktop-4.1-noarch:languages-4.1-amd64:languages-4.1-noarch:printing-4.1-amd64:printing-4.1-noarch</span><br><span class="line">Distributor ID: CentOS</span><br><span class="line">Description:    CentOS Linux release 7.3.1611 (Core) </span><br><span class="line">Release:        7.3.1611</span><br><span class="line">Codename:       Core</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">36.103.245.135 | SUCCESS | rc=0 &gt;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">LSB Version:    :core-4.1-amd64:core-4.1-noarch:cxx-4.1-amd64:cxx-4.1-noarch:languages-4.1-amd64:languages-4.1-noarch:printing-4.1-amd64:printing-4.1-noarch</span><br><span class="line">Distributor ID: CentOS</span><br><span class="line">Description:    CentOS Linux release 7.3.1611 (Core) </span><br><span class="line">Release:        7.3.1611</span><br><span class="line">Codename:       Core</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="【示例2】为所有服务器安装ntp服务-并设置为开机启动"><a href="#【示例2】为所有服务器安装ntp服务-并设置为开机启动" class="headerlink" title="【示例2】为所有服务器安装ntp服务,并设置为开机启动"></a>【示例2】为所有服务器安装ntp服务,并设置为开机启动</h3><h4 id="步骤1：安装ntp服务"><a href="#步骤1：安装ntp服务" class="headerlink" title="步骤1：安装ntp服务"></a>步骤1：安装ntp服务</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@Ansible ~]# ansible all -s -m yum -a &quot;name=ntp state=present&quot;</span><br><span class="line">36.103.245.138 | SUCCESS =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;changed&quot;: false, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;msg&quot;: &quot;&quot;, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;rc&quot;: 0, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;results&quot;: [</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;ntp-4.2.6p5-28.el7.centos.x86_64 providing ntp is already installed&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">36.103.245.70 | SUCCESS =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;changed&quot;: false, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;msg&quot;: &quot;&quot;, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;rc&quot;: 0, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;results&quot;: [</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;ntp-4.2.6p5-28.el7.centos.x86_64 providing ntp is already installed&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">36.103.245.135 | SUCCESS =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;changed&quot;: false, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;msg&quot;: &quot;&quot;, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;rc&quot;: 0, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;results&quot;: [</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;ntp-4.2.6p5-28.el7.centos.x86_64 providing ntp is already installed&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="步骤2：启动ntp服务-并设置为开机启动"><a href="#步骤2：启动ntp服务-并设置为开机启动" class="headerlink" title="步骤2：启动ntp服务,并设置为开机启动"></a>步骤2：启动ntp服务,并设置为开机启动</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@Ansible ~]# ansible all -m service -a &quot;name=ntpd state=started enabled=yes&quot;</span><br><span class="line">36.103.245.138 | SUCCESS =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;changed&quot;: false, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;enabled&quot;: true, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;name&quot;: &quot;ntpd&quot;, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;state&quot;: &quot;started&quot;, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;status&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ......</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">36.103.245.70 | SUCCESS =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;changed&quot;: false, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;enabled&quot;: true, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;name&quot;: &quot;ntpd&quot;, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;state&quot;: &quot;started&quot;, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;status&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ......</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">36.103.245.135 | SUCCESS =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;changed&quot;: false, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;enabled&quot;: true, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;name&quot;: &quot;ntpd&quot;, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;state&quot;: &quot;started&quot;, </span><br><span class="line">    &quot;status&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ......</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
